name: Kate Ryan
description:
Hello my dear
Compliments of the season my good friend. I am Dr. Kate Ryan, British medical doctor, Consultant Haematologist. Chair General Haematology Task Force of British Committee for Standards in Haematology. I wish to extend my friendship to you. May be you will be the first to make me travel down to your country. Let me know more about you and also send me your photos. As time goes on, we will know more about ourselves. Wishing you a prosperous new year.
email… kateryan.uk@hotmail.com
Dr. Kate Ryan
